ContentDesc_Sephirot: The faux commander fancies a tale featuring the most massive of monstrosities, which immediately puts you in mind of Sephirot's talent for spontaneous growth. Let the seeds of memory take root, and relive the moment when one false step meant being crushed into paste by an oak-sized limb...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_9901_Text: Pestilent northerners... You shall regret the decision to loosen my fetters!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_9902_Text: The equilibrium of life... I shall tip thy scales and partake of thy bounteous energy!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_9903_Text: Patience and penance... For millennia have I yearned to enact this vengeance!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_9904_Text: I am the end and the beginning! By my touch shall your wretched lives be blessed!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_9905_Text: I am the incarnation of life! I cannot perish...cannot wither...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_9906_Text: To die here is a mercy... You shall not witness your lands when I rend them asunder!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_9907_Text: You have dimmed my boundless light. What power of death do you mortals wield...?
